Welcome to a new YouTube channel: Dark Brown! 
Dark Brown is a channel featuring a variety of content exploring stories of women by women. Head on over to our YouTube channel (link in bio) to give us a like!
Happy watching!

Welcome to my Dark Brown channel! This is just a little quick intro to this new channel!
I'm proud to announce a channel showcasing stories of women and by women through the art of filmmaking. What does this mean exactly? I'm a filmmaker, actress, and writer and I love to create content (shorts, sketches, skits, etc.) expressing the complexity of womanhood. Most of all, I'm excited to collaborate with other artists (especially female artists) to create new and interesting content for this channel!
Happy watching!
With much love and gratitude,
Keisha Bissram
